</description><media:thumbnail url="https://s.rfi.fr/media/display/aa9067e2-0aff-11ec-99be-005056a90284/w:1024/p:16x9/e99fa9e59bbde9809ae8bf87e4bfaee4be8be38080e7a681e6ada2e88bb9e69e9ce8b0b7e6ad8ce59e84e696ade6898be69cbae694afe4bb98.jpg"/><enclosure url="https://s.rfi.fr/media/display/aa9067e2-0aff-11ec-99be-005056a90284/w:1024/p:16x9/e99fa9e59bbde9809ae8bf87e4bfaee4be8be38080e7a681e6ada2e88bb9e69e9ce8b0b7e6ad8ce59e84e696ade6898be69cbae694afe4bb98.jpg" type="image/jpeg" length="0"/><guid isPermaLink="false">0f6d1a70-0b00-11ec-91c4-005056bf762b</guid><pubDate>Wed, 01 Sep 2021 10:25:54 GMT</pubDate><dc:creator>夏榕</dc:creator></item><item><category>中國</category><title>克里應邀訪問中國 北京或有意作出新的承諾？</title><link>https://www.rfi.fr/tw/%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B/20210901-%E5%85%8B%E9%87%8C%E6%87%89%E9%82%80%E8%A8%AA%E5%95%8F%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B-%E5%8C%97%E4%BA%AC%E6%88%96%E6%9C%89%E6%84%8F%E4%BD%9C%E5%87%BA%E6%96%B0%E7%9A%84%E6%89%BF%E8%AB%BE</link><description>
